				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Very nice! You have a real skill for sculpting a slice of world.<br />
Lovely piece of writing.</p>
<p>I also had problems with the comma rush in the second paragraph. Doing the take-a-breath thing could turn your face blue! Ahem.<br />
The I-ing at the end didn&#8217;t quite work for me. I liked the more anonymous narrator.<br />
But both are minor niggles and I really enjoyed the story.<br />
